{
  "stem": "5654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were scared to say to the doctor that we were sick for fear that, you know, maybe you weren't telling the truth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, in the-- in wintertime, we used to, we always wore-- in those days, kids never wore long- long pants.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we used to have chilblain in the back here when we used to walk in the snow and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, you know, at night time, the dormitory windows used to open up that were French windows.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The snow used to fall in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And even though we were cold, that was part of the upbringing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we had also bathrooms, you know, showers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once a week-- once a week, they'd put on the hot water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The rest of the time, we were told to wash ourself in cold water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And before we went out of the bathroom, they used to check the back of ours ears, on our knee, everywhere on our foot, that we washed ourself properly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, I must say that, for that, cleanliness was very important.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, they had to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Otherwise there'd be, people, you know, would be sick and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So looking back, that was a good idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because even today, I've learned, I've even taught my kids to be-- [LAUGHS] to be extremely tidy and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they used to check.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, once we were having breakfast, they used to come and put their hands in our bed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if the bed was still warm, they'd make it undone and tell us, go upstairs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And next time, make sure that your bed is aerated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the corner of the bed, it had to be perfectly square, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The corners had to be done properly.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
